## 💰 Financial Model & Math

### Pilot Unit Economics (Per Station, Month 1–6)

#### Revenue Model

| Plan | Price | Est. Members (Pilot) | Monthly Revenue |
|---|---|---|---|
| Unlimited Wash | $39.99/mo | 80 | $3,199 |
| Basic Wash (4/mo) | $19.99/mo | 40 | $799 |
| **Total MRR per station** | | **120** | **$3,998** |

#### Cost Model (Per Station)

| Cost Item | Monthly Cost | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| SaaS platform fee (operator) | $199 | FuelFlow subscription |
| Fuel discount subsidy | $480 | 120 members × 20 gal avg × $0.20 |
| Promo/coupon cost est. | $120 | ~$1/member redeemed |
| Payment processing (2.9%) | $116 | On $3,998 revenue |
| **Total Costs** | **$915** | |
| **Net per Station/Month** | **$3,083** | Operator keeps this |

> ✅ **Math Check:** $3,998 revenue − $915 costs = **$3,083 net/station/month**
> At 120 members × $39.99 avg blended ≈ **$3,998** ✓

#### FuelFlow Revenue (SaaS)

| Revenue Stream | Per Station/Mo | 10 Stations | 100 Stations |
|---|---|---|---|
| SaaS platform fee | $199 | $1,990 | $19,900 |
| Transaction fee (1%) | $40 | $400 | $4,000 |
| **FuelFlow MRR** | **$239** | **$2,390** | **$23,900** |

#### Payback Period

```
Operator setup cost (onboarding + signage): ~$500 one-time
Monthly net gain: $3,083
Payback period: $500 / $3,083 = 0.16 months ≈ 5 days ✓
```

#### 12-Month Projection (3-Station Pilot → Scale)

| Month | Stations | Total Members | FuelFlow MRR | Cumulative ARR |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| 1–3 | 3 | 360 | $717 | $2,151 |
| 4–6 | 10 | 1,200 | $2,390 | $14,340 |
| 7–9 | 25 | 3,000 | $5,975 | $53,775 |
| 10–12 | 50 | 6,000 | $11,950 | $143,400 |

> ✅ **Year 1 ARR at 50 stations: ~$143,400** (conservative, no upsell)

#### Customer Lifetime Value (CLV)

```
Average monthly revenue per member:  $39.99
Average churn rate (target):          5%/month
Average member lifetime:              1 / 0.05 = 20 months

CLV = $39.99 × 20 = $799.80 per member

CAC target (referral + in-store):     $15–25
LTV:CAC ratio:                        ~32:1 ✓ (healthy = >3:1)
```

#### Fuel Discount Math Check

```
Members: 120 per station
Avg fill-up frequency: 2× per month
Avg gallons per fill: 10 gal
Total gallons/month: 120 × 2 × 10 = 2,400 gal
Discount per gallon: $0.20
Total monthly discount subsidy: 2,400 × $0.20 = $480 ✓
```

